{"tid":2350711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「居安抗疫」程式未能啟動，台灣返港女子質疑檢疫成效","createTime":"2021-01-02T14:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T14:10:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"adf2c25c1922d41a2394b7dc0e9a8e3d5ec7a860","tid":2350711,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yznTrvIX6LENTKNXaogVyQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/uGuiprNl9qoJBO0U0cj.jQ--~B/aD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/4500bb06bfb24bb9ace427af9a0f7fa3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyznTrvIX6LENTKNXaogVyQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS41Mzg0NjE1Mzg0NjE1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuGuiprNl9qoJBO0U0cj.jQ--~B%2FaD01NTc7dz03ODA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F4500bb06bfb24bb9ace427af9a0f7fa3&h=d5715ac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb05Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=5dfa96be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】外地抵港人士在檢疫期間需要佩戴電子手環及啟動「居安抗疫」流動應用程式，讓政府監察他們在檢疫期間有否擅離檢疫地點。不過，一名台灣返港女子在社交媒體表示，昨(1日)回家後嘗試啟動「居安抗疫」應用程式，但先後6次均未能啟動，並彈出「發生錯誤」的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n事主主動致電熱線求助，並留下電話跟姓名，今晨(2日)有政府人員致電她，先後3次要求她嘗試重新啟動程式，又叫她重新下載程式，惟人員表示仍收不到信號，多次要求事主重新安裝及啟動。至中午12時，事主仍未能成功啟動程式。<br />\n<br />\n事主慨嘆：「如果是其他人，搞不好昨天根本不會自行通報」，懷疑電子手環可能「有問題」，質疑檢疫成效，坦言對今次事件感無奈。她亦有分享她在台灣的防疫經驗，指台灣是「用手機啟動電子圍籬」，並不需要像港府一樣大肆購買電子手環。她建議購買電子手環、維護程式及人員工資可用來設立「防疫計程車」。<br />\n<br />\n政府資訊科技總監辦公室發言人回應說，如檢疫人士未有在指定時間內啟動電子手環，資科辦人員會與他們聯絡，提供協助，包括派員上門協助啟動電子手環。若未能與檢疫人士聯絡，或懷疑他們離開指定地點，資科辦會通知衞生署和警方跟進。截至上月底，創新及科技局共派發約41萬個電子手環給檢疫人士使用，電子手環及「居安抗疫」流動應用程式相關開支共涉約190萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sWLw0Agw.j8EKEB4sC.98Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE3MDcuMDc2OTIzMDc2OTIz/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/I90KCjL4a.IZFOxnhmEz.A--~B/aD0xMzg3O3c9NzgwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/1ccca960449633e1ac22e7de649b7129\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsWLw0Agw.j8EKEB4sC.98Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE3MDcuMDc2OTIzMDc2OTIz%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FI90KCjL4a.IZFOxnhmEz.A--~B%2FaD0xMzg3O3c9NzgwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F1ccca960449633e1ac22e7de649b7129&h=b17702bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5f8cde7510062be2395cbba2deb6c2a348416a4","tid":2350711,"uid":7323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:07:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">用d錢整d垃圾出來</span>"},{"pid":"63ff84e7665a87d254f857ca305dc41b36edd9f1","tid":2350711,"uid":345689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾到<br />\n浪費晒納稅人啲錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db776ac0f84ab50265bb959df2195fff814b31f","tid":2350711,"uid":129676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:10:29.000Z","msg":"隻錶邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}